- [master_chain.rs] Fix hardcoded 44100 sample rate → read from input file
- [master_chain.rs] Improve apply_recommendation() documentation

NEW FILES:
- [README.md] Full project documentation with architecture, features, setup instructions

Signed-off-by: BMAD Team (Mary/Sarah/Winston/Devon/Quinn)
